---
By: Hsu Yin
Source:
  ISBN: 978-1571746931
  Locus:
    Page: 191
  Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
---
Water and mind are both still.
Sun and moon reflect brightly.
Now and then a mist drifts across
my mirror like a cloud.
For a moment this confuses me,
but then I remember.
